record.title: REMOVAL OF NAME OF MEMBER AS COSPONSOR OF H.R. 946
record.narrative:
REMOVAL OF NAME OF MEMBER AS COSPONSOR OF H.R. 946 -- (House of Representatives - September 27, 2007)

[Page: H11008]

speaking.paragraph: Mr. Speaker, I ask unanimous consent to remove Representative Emanuel Cleaver as a cosponsor of H.R. 946, the Consumer Overdraft Protection Fair Practices Act. He was added to the bill in error.

record.chair: Is there objection to the request of the gentlewoman from New York?
